    <briefdescription>
<para>Handling time components </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The TickTimerService allows your app to be called every time one Time component has changed. This is extremely important for watchfaces. Your app can choose on which time component change a tick should occur. Time components are defined by a <ref refid="group___tick_timer_service_1ga0423d00e0eb199de523a92031b5a1107" kindref="member">TimeUnits</ref> enum bitmask. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
